{"tid":138991,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人仲記得細個有本叫天馬行空嘅月刊","createTime":"2017-03-01T05:06:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T11:45:52.000Z","uid":60398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e868951037db1a2939747c29b277616c22abf78c","tid":138991,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T05:06:48.000Z","msg":"唔知仲有無人記得<br />\n我細個期期都求啊媽買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依加搬完屋 渣都無得淨 <br />\n每期有啲星座野啊<br />\n配音員訪問啊<br />\n無聊冷知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然漫畫好濕鳩 成日都skip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但諗返起 好想佢繼續出 <br />\n有無人有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5870b6840a35a000349ce0bd9e10ef35aca81d16","tid":138991,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T05:07:29.000Z","msg":"有印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3e8bd13054f3110cf4da0601dd987a12947899","tid":138991,"uid":65538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T05:08:10.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由佢地出既第一期追到最後一期<br />\n成日都抽獎但淨係抽中過一個file"},{"pid":"4aaeaf7165fce8fe681e646fd7c52b4fc6abec30","tid":138991,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T05:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由佢地出既第一期追到最後一期<br />\n成日都抽獎但淨係抽中過一個file</blockquote><br />\n我好似係第三期開始追 個陣送hunter 手錶<br />\n但其實每期都贈品都幾有意思 特別係啲週年號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f24cb44ae57e8123c99eafedb320472f4ade2190","tid":138991,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T05:16:16.000Z","msg":"記得開頭嗰幾期又送彈珠人又剩，<br />\n個勢仲以為有力同coco一戰"},{"pid":"d709717c43168